Name: LGC Power-Up/Down
checklistText:
<size=21>LGC POWER-UP</size>

1.
	PANEL 11:	CB PGNS:	LGC/DSKY - close
	PANEL 1:	Poss LGC warn lt - on (up to 20 sec)

2.	PANEL 4:	Key RSET

3.	CHECKLIST: Fresh Start

<size=21>LGC POWER-DOWN</size>

1.	Key V37E 06E

2.	FL V50 N25 - Checklist reference
		Rl 00062 - Switch LGC power down
		R2 -----
		R3 -----
	Key PRO until STBY lt - on

3.	(optional)
	PANEL 11: CB PGNS: LGC/DSKY - open
	MASTER ALARM - on
	LGC warn lt - on
	MASTER ALARM pb/lt - reset
